      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GAMBELLA (4) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at Sandown, scoring by 5 lengths (33.91). Expected to go close again. WARM COCKLES (1) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 600m behind Lochinvar Hummer (34.99) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Has ability and can atone. PAW IKE (2) ran a good time (34.52) when placing three back at this track but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing fourth (34.59) at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. TEXAS PRESIDENT (3) was prominent throughout when successful last start. Sure to run well again.",
